Description: OpenCog cognitive architecture framework (runtime)
 OpenCog is an open-source software project aimed at directly confronting
 the AGI challenge, using mathematical and biological inspiration and
 professional software engineering techniques.
 .
 This package contains the main OpenCog framework including:
  - GHOST: Goal-Oriented Script-based Hierarchical Organizing System for Thought
  - NLP: Natural Language Processing tools
  - EVA: Emotional/Expressive Animation system
  - OpenPsi: Motivational and emotional system
  - Neighbors: Similarity and clustering algorithms
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries for runtime use.

Package: libopencog-dev
Section: libdevel
